longName: iShares Trust - iShares U.S. Real Estate ETF
longBusinessSummary: iShares Trust - iShares U.S. Real Estate ETF is an exchange traded fund launched by BlackRock, Inc. It is managed by BlackRock Fund Advisors. The fund invests in public equity markets of the United States. The fund invests in stocks of companies operating across real estate sectors. It invests in growth and value stocks of companies across diversified market capitalization. It seeks to track the performance of the Dow Jones U.S. Real Estate Capped Index, by using representative sampling technique. iShares Trust - iShares U.S. Real Estate ETF was formed on June 12, 2000 and is domiciled in the United States.
